{"tid":2273023,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"恒生大學新取錄計劃 只重才華不理DSE成績","createTime":"2020-11-05T12:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T03:52:51.000Z","uid":225931,"like":20,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bcfbe6a64648c7d7df7b9374fee679cc25919f","tid":2273023,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"香港恒生大學重整「校長推薦計劃」，直接取錄有潛力的中學生，讓他們免去應考文憑試之苦，直升大學發揮所長。該校校長何順文接受訪問時表示，初步擬撥不多於5%學額，在放榜前直接取錄具特殊才華的學生，每所中學限一個名額，詳情有待公布。<br />\n<br />\n何指，恒大打算推出新校長推薦計劃，並本月內正式通過。合資格學生申請後，會考慮學生的才華能力、校內成績，經面試甄選後，不論文憑試成績如何均會直接取錄。他指，每間中學校長可推薦一名學生申請，才華及課程範疇亦毋須對應，但需獲一定校內成績。"},{"pid":"f7c72a1b47041d2484f0360721df10a0f954b016","tid":2273023,"uid":367151,"like":293,"dislike":2,"score":291,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:25:59.000Z","msg":"有才華會讀恆大？"},{"pid":"b99765262270d3babd7d7c9c0e1b35435dc8aa2c","tid":2273023,"uid":118502,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"quote":{"pid":"f7c72a1b47041d2484f0360721df10a0f954b016","tid":2273023,"uid":367151,"like":293,"dislike":2,"score":291,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:25:59.000Z","msg":"有才華會讀恆大？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"才華唔係讀書到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beaec1aa876a6f1545293ec1d27d7e9e2410825","tid":2273023,"uid":126510,"like":53,"dislike":4,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"b99765262270d3babd7d7c9c0e1b35435dc8aa2c","tid":2273023,"uid":118502,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"quote":{"pid":"f7c72a1b47041d2484f0360721df10a0f954b016","tid":2273023,"uid":367151,"like":293,"dislike":2,"score":291,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:25:59.000Z","msg":"有才華會讀恆大？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"才華唔係讀書到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3